            <description><![CDATA[【⚠️<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E7%AD%89%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%E8%A6%81%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%B3%E6%89%93120%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E7%AD%89%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%E8%A6%81%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%B3%E6%89%93120%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#这些症状不能等消失要立即打120#</span></a>】卒中俗称“中风”，我国卒中患病总人数超2800万，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E4%B8%8D%E8%A7%84%E5%BE%8B%E7%AD%89%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E5%8D%92%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%91%E7%97%85%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E5%8C%96%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E4%B8%8D%E8%A7%84%E5%BE%8B%E7%AD%89%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E5%8D%92%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%91%E7%97%85%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E5%8C%96%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#睡眠不规律等导致卒中发病年轻化#</span></a>。①协调和平衡能力丧失导致行走困难或摔倒；②视力下降看不清楚；③丧失意识无法控制地抽搐；④一侧肢体突然无力或麻木；⑤无法正常说话或理解他人语言意思，面部麻木或口角歪斜等，出现这些症状，请立即拨打120👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4970832301326373" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hk3pbm7i66j61xt13ahdt02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/LY4NazAtlx08amNpgp9S01041201nRxU0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1BThihd3VLAY5R&amp;Expires=1700687570&amp;ssig=Gxxea6qbc0&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https:/