        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[[看书]#高嘌呤食物排行榜# 这些蔬菜竟是隐形的“嘌呤大户”[吃惊]👇🏻[星星]食用菌类：每100克的菌类嘌呤含量普遍在100毫克以上，每100克香菇中的嘌呤甚至达...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[[看书]<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%AB%98%E5%98%8C%E5%91%A4%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E6%8E%92%E8%A1%8C%E6%A6%9C%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%AB%98%E5%98%8C%E5%91%A4%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E6%8E%92%E8%A1%8C%E6%A6%9C%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#高嘌呤食物排行榜#</span></a> 这些蔬菜竟是隐形的“嘌呤大户”<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>👇🏻<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>食用菌类：<br>每100克的菌类嘌呤含量普遍在100毫克以上，每100克香菇中的嘌呤甚至达到了320毫克；<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>豆类：<br>每100克大豆含有约160毫克的嘌呤；<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>十字花科类：<br>菜花、西蓝花等十字花科类蔬菜，会让尿酸结晶更快堆积在体内，引发痛风发作，建议高尿酸患者焯水后再烹调食用；<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>春笋：<br>每100克的芦笋尖中，嘌呤含量接近500毫克，是芦笋根茎的5倍以上；<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>紫菜：<br>过度摄入容易增加体内的尿酸含量；<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[星星]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/x_star1-e5d754c7b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>菠菜：<br>每100克的菠菜含有约90毫克的嘌呤。此外，菠菜含有较多的草酸，容易和钙一起生成草酸钙沉积在关节处，导致痛风结石。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（广东疾控）<img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk3po27u9rj20j10h30tu.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
            <pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 03:16:07 GMT</pubDate>
